snippet.textDisplay:
Did people notice that in 2 recent finales Coke Studio Season 10 & Lux Style Awards 2017 the same JJ song " Us Rah Par" was sung in different rhythms dedicated to him & his legacy but the resonating msg coming from JJ (thru his lyrics & indeed his life) is  "mesmerizing" & "urging" his fans and his singing colleagues to leave this  path of "Angaar" (Fire) 

JJ left too soon but his subliminal msg comes across .....

Hum Kyun Chalein
Us Rah Par
Jis Rah Par
Sab hee chalein
Kyun Na Chunein
Woh raasta
Jis par nahin
Koi gaya

Dil udaas nazrein udaas
Dilbar nahin agar aas paas
Din raat aah bharna
Aur beqaraar rehna
Yeh khail hai beqaar hai
Kuch bhi nahin angaar hai
Is aag main jalein kyun
Pal pal jiyein marein kyun

It's deep JJ but we got your msg :(

May Allah bless u and bring us to the Right path. Aameen
